properties.description: Introducing an exquisite residential masterpiece, a collection of 15 newly built 4-bedroom semi-detached duplexes with a BQ (Boys' Quarter), nestled in the heart of Nigeria's vibrant cityscape. This architectural marvel seamlessly blends contemporary design with luxurious comfort, offering an unparalleled living experience for discerning individuals and families. Each unit of this splendid development boasts a spacious and well-thought-out floor plan, spanning across multiple levels to provide abundant living space. The ground floor greets you with a grand entrance leading to a tastefully designed living area, adorned with high ceilings and large windows that allow natural light to flood the interior. The thoughtfully placed dining area creates a seamless flow, perfect for hosting gatherings and creating lasting memories.
